Item 15.Exhibits, Financial Statement Schedules
(a) The following documents are filed as a part of this 10-K:
1. Financial Statements
The following financial statements are included in Part II, Item 8 of this 10-K:
•Consolidated Statements of Earnings for the fiscal years ended September 27, 2020, September 29, 2019, and September 30, 2018;
•Consolidated Statements of Comprehensive Income for the fiscal years ended September 27, 2020, September 29, 2019, and September 30, 2018;
•Consolidated Balance Sheets as of September 27, 2020 and September 29, 2019;
•Consolidated Statements of Cash Flows for the fiscal years ended September 27, 2020, September 29, 2019, and September 30, 2018;
•Consolidated Statements of Equity for the fiscal years ended September 27, 2020, September 29, 2019, and September 30, 2018;
•Notes to Consolidated Financial Statements; and
•Reports of Independent Registered Public Accounting Firm
2. Financial Statement Schedules
Financial statement schedules are omitted because they are not required or are not applicable, or the required information is provided in the consolidated financial statements or notes described in Item 15(a)(1) above.
3. Exhibits
* Denotes a management contract or compensatory plan or arrangement.
** Furnished herewith.
